    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Refers to the period in Egypt from about 750 to 656 BCE during which Kushite rulers held power. The period is characterized by a return to monumentality, a high quality of craftsmanship, and archaizing tendencies especially in sculpture.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000040221/Trigger et al., Ancient Egypt (1983)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Se refiere al período en Egipto desde aproximadamente el 750 al 656 a.C durante el que los gobernantes Kushite mantuvieron el poder. El período se caracteriza por un retorno a la monumentalidad, una alta calidad de arte y tendencias arcaizantes sobre todo en escultura.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Verwijst naar de periode in Egypte van circa 750 tot 656 v. Chr. tijdens de Kushite overheersing. De periode kenmerkt zich door een terugkeer naar de monumentaliteit, groot vakmanschap, en archaïserende tendensen, met name in de sculptuur.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>指自西元前750年至西元前656年間，庫希特人（Kushite）統治下的埃及時代。此時代的特色是紀念性建築物的興建，高品質的工藝技術，以及特別可見於雕塑上的仿古風潮。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000079740/AS-Academia Sinica data (2014-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
    </Descriptive_Notes>
